{"tid":386331,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"To:壓力大失眠嘅你，ASMR可能幫到你","createTime":"2017-09-03T19:10:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T03:47:43.000Z","uid":143456,"like":33,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ac332c60c1e944353d1873a3b68a519e6ba6ea76","tid":386331,"uid":143456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T19:10:34.000Z","msg":"有時唔知點解會失眠,係張床典?典去又?唔著真係好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢幾個月我迷上左一樣叫<span style=\"color: red;\">ASMR</span>?野，因為佢真係好似?安眠藥咁樣整到你極快?著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，甚至我懷疑ASMR係有毒，因為我唔聽，就會好難?得著,直頭好似吸毒上癮咁樣。<br />\n<br />\n見到對解決失眠咁有效，如果我唔同大家講下我真係正仆街呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我平時會去YOUTUBE搵ASMR?呢聽，不過我唔會聽死一個，因為ASMR有個缺點就係會好快失效,會腦好快對呢?聲音有&quot;抗藥性&quot; 所以我會成日轉。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n起度我想推介番我認為比較正?YOUTUBER做?ASMR，不過你聽之前一定要準備耳機，最好係入耳式果隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一個:<span style=\"color: blue;\">MassageASMR</span><br />\nMassageASMR係我第一個聽ASMR?人,佢拍?ASMR片種有好多，<span style=\"color: purple;\">捽膠袋</span>，<span style=\"color: purple;\">按摩</span>，<span style=\"color: purple;\">無人聲系列</span>，同埋佢最大?特點係佢拍好多條片都係<span style=\"color: purple;\">極少底噪</span>，對於我呢?唔鍾意底噪?人，確實係一大福音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 再加上佢一條片去有好多種玩法，另外，起行雷閃電?夜晚可以聽有佢把聲?片，佢磁性?聲音足以令你安心?個好覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n佢其中一條片: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=68SWV9UplWc&amp;index=2&amp;list=PL1OPyJWm858Iu1OdsPRs8m_UASKAdWT9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D68SWV9UplWc%26index%3D2%26list%3DPL1OPyJWm858Iu1OdsPRs8m_UASKAdWT9F&d=eSihygRt4ZE%2FMn2LPEVkfi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=f15c0e20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=68SWV9UplWc&amp;index=2&amp;list=PL1OPyJWm858Iu1OdsPRs8m_UASKAdWT9F</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二個:<span style=\"color: pink;\">hatomugi ASMR</span><br />\nhatomugi ASMR呢個日本女我就冇乜留意佢把聲，不過唔代表佢唔吸引，佢其中有一條<span style=\"color: pink;\">捽耳仔</span>片，係我暫時可以一個禮拜聽三似都唔厭?片，仲有佢一條用化妝掃掃耳仔?片都爽死我,所以我都幾推介佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n <span style=\"color: pink;\">捽耳仔片</span>:<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=88zbsuvAyQg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D88zbsuvAyQg&d=eSihygRt4ZE%2FMn2LPEVkfi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=4183313d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=88zbsuvAyQg</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">化妝掃掃耳仔</span>:<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nKjz95M-twU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnKjz95M-twU&d=eSihygRt4ZE%2FMn2LPEVkfi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=a5d912e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nKjz95M-twU</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第三個:<span style=\"color: brown;\">asmr zeitgeist</span><br />\nasmr zeitgeist佢拍<span style=\"color: brown;\">玩水玩膠粒</span>?片好出色，我認為佢做?水聲同膠粒聲暫時冇人能及，同樣<span style=\"color: brown;\">冇底噪</span>?佢更顯得佢功力十足!<br />\n玩水玩膠粒:<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x0nvMBpLiIM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dx0nvMBpLiIM&d=eSihygRt4ZE%2FMn2LPEVkfi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=300371b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x0nvMBpLiIM</a><br />\n<br />\n第四個:Whitewinterwhispers<br />\nWhitewinterwhispers 我只會介紹一條片，就係芬蘭話急口令，一邊聽佢細細聲起你耳邊嘰哩咕嚕一邊睇佢唔錯?顏值呢?，都係一仲享受<br />\n<br />\n芬蘭話急口令:<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Nh0pHvFsmng\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DNh0pHvFsmng&d=eSihygRt4ZE%2FMn2LPEVkfi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=84efd5d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Nh0pHvFsmng</a><br />\n<br />\n最後，我仲想介紹一條片係同ASMR冇關，而且係純音樂，不過都可以幫你入睡。有樣野唔同?係,我唔建議呢個用耳機聽，你地試下用喇叭聽，感覺會立體好多。<br />\n純音樂: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UXgqDlrqmzo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DUXgqDlrqmzo&d=eSihygRt4ZE%2FMn2LPEVkfi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=eec37cb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UXgqDlrqmzo</a><br />\n<br />\n以上就係我所介紹?ASMR片，希望你地都會迷上佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3809a08adef2e06f3446ee4654f6eaab3ea21860","tid":386331,"uid":143456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T19:18:03.000Z","msg":"如果你地都覺得正嘅，不妨留個言<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"934f12edce599d34f5176679671d74cfda43b56b","tid":386331,"uid":58505,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T19:35:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/biH8zewSRIc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbiH8zewSRIc&d=eSihygRt4ZE%2FMn2LPEVkfi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=fc49e565\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/biH8zewSRIc</a><br />\nDr.t<br />\n把聲好正"},{"pid":"223192c2dfef0aa3dc777b9cfc5f673d1aedd183","tid":386331,"uid":143456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T19:51:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/biH8zewSRIc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbiH8zewSRIc&d=eSihygRt4ZE%2FMn2LPEVkfi7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=fc49e565\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/biH8zewSRIc</a><br />\nDr.t<br />\n把聲好正</blockquote><br />\n正，我鍾意佢啲的的聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20939f408ba5368c6a87ca67192d79fe5ad40ca4","tid":386331,"uid":60170,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T19:56:49.000Z","msg":"ASMR Suns<br />\nPPOMO ASMR<br />\nFuwaHime ASMR<br />\nLatte ASMR<br />\nASMR Joureny<br />\nMaple ASMR<br />\n全部私人喜好"},{"pid":"d5d06d00a69a300f62f7cceee6e0159ba5a2fc19